        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Cleanup tunables",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Cleanup tunables\n\nKfilnd had defined but unused module parameters. In addition, kfilnd\ntunables based on the o2iblnd tunables. Clean up all this to have a\nset of module parameters and tunables that are either used by kfilnd\nor LNet.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9382\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I9b02539cd57d8b0b779c990f3426df8325b821ae\n"
